content: I'm a semi-seasoned chat captain for phone banks, but when I try to sign up for shifts, the registration site only shows me slots through the end of August. Does anyone know how to get the September shift calendar to show up?
Hi! We are working on adding more dates and times, please be patient and check back in later!
Also this is a question that  <#1270924834163134564> should be best able to help with
You should now be able to access all vote team channels!
